# Changelog

All notable changes to BeautifyAds are documented here.

## [1.0.0] – 2026-06-02

Initial public release.

### Features
- Reorganized left menu – Keywords, Search terms, Assets, and Videos grouped under Campaigns
- Reorganized flyout menu (hover-over icon-rail menu) with matching structure
- Toggle individual menu items on/off from the extension popup
- Hide AI Max promo block in search campaign settings
- Hide Recommendations notifications and Insights blocks
- `G` then `L` hotkey to jump to Search terms
- One-click Active toggle to instantly see the original Google Ads layout
- Status badge on Google Ads pages